<h1>Area of Kite</h1>
<p>Area of kite is the space enclosed by a kite. A kite is a quadrilateral =
in which two pairs of adjacent sides are equal. The elements of a kite are =
its 4 angles, its 4 sides, and 2 diagonals. In this article, we will focus =
on the area of a kite and its formula.</p>
