<sub>1</sub> and (d)<sub>2</sub> are long and short diagonals of a kite.</p=
><p>The area of any kite let's say ABCD with diagonal AC and BD is given as=
 =C2=BD =C3=97 AC =C3=97 BD.</p></div></div></div><div itemscope=3D"" class=
